page.title: 13PROFILE
page.content:
NAME:Mac AGE:37
Gets up at 8.00 am and eats his Breakfast at 8.10 am.He has 2 slices of toast and strong coffee.He leaves for work at 8.40 am.He works at Washington where he is a managing director of a small engineering company.Likes talking to the customers best.He has his dinner at 12.30 pm normally he has a salad and a cup of coffee after.Coming home varies,normally it is about 7.00 pm.When he comes in he relaxes and has his tea.He then does financial quotations for the next day.At about 9.00 pm he watches the television,his favourite programmes are Scientific and Documentaries.He has a sandwich at 11.00 pm,watches television and goes to bed at 12.30 am.
